<body class="is-deco">
  <header class="l-header">
    <div class="l-header__inner">
      <a href="https://stock-sun.com/coaching/" class="l-header__logo img">
        <img src="https://stock-sun.com/coaching/wp-content/themes/stocksun_lp_theme/assets/img/common/logo.svg" alt="StockSun株式会社">
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="l-engineer section">
      <div class="inner _wide">
        <div class="l-engineer__container">
          <div class="l-engineer__body">
            <h1 class="ttl">StockSunの現役エンジニアによる<br>コーチング型プログラミングスクール！</h1>
            <div class="engineer-slider__container">
              <div class="swiper-container engineer-slider" id="engineerSlider">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper engineer-slider__wrapper">
                  <div class="swiper-slide  engineer-slider__slide">
                    <div id="player0"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide  engineer-slider__slide">
                    <div id="player1"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide  engineer-slider__slide">
                    <div id="player2"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide  engineer-slider__slide">
                    <div id="player3"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="engineer-slider__prev"></div>
              <div class="engineer-slider__next"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="txt l-engineer__txt-box is-active">
              <span class="strong">【テックエリートが選ばれる4つの理由】</span><br>
              ・実案件と同じ開発に挑むようなカリキュラム<br>・経験豊富な現役エンジニアがマンツーマンで丁寧に指導<br>・制作した課題に対して報酬を贈呈（提出期限あり）<br>・卒業後に案件獲得までサポート（発注実績多数）
              <br><br>
              <span class="strong">【コース紹介】</span><br>
